public abstract class CCDataBuilder<T extends Bean,B extends CCDataBuilder<T,B>> extends DataBuilder<T,B>
Superclass for all ClaimCenter data builders. This superclass adds a special BeanPopulator as the first step of the builder after the bean instantiation. This populator checks whether the current DataGenContext is a perf context, and if so it runs the bean through the TestEntityPopulator in order to prepopulate the bean's fields.
Author:
jdonahue
